videos.description: Tariq Owens dunks an alley-oop pass for Texas Tech, then Ochai Agbaji slams down the lob pass at the other end for Kansas.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Texas Tech, Kansas trade alley-oop dunks) 2019/02/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Texas Tech, Kansas trade alley-oop dunks

videos.description: Kansas freshman Devon Dotson is left all alone by the Texas Tech defense and he takes advantage with a 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Kansas' Dotson buries wide-open 3-pointer

videos.description: Ochai Agbaji cuts down the baseline and Charlie Moore finds him with an alley-oop to extend Kansas' lead.
videos.headline: Agbaji flushes down oop
